Detailed Description

Request to be used when searching using a coordinate and distance sorting.

The request will search the whole countr. <br /> FIXME: Expand id:s of regions <br /> FIXME: Currently the whole country is always searched. <br />

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum ClosestSearchRequest::state_t [private]
 

Describes what to do.

Enumeration values:
FINDING_COUNTRY  Uses CoordinateRequest to find the country of the coordinate.
TOP_REGION  Uses TopRegionRequest to find the maps of the current country.
SEARCHING  Waits for the searchPackets to arrive.
ERROR  The request is done, but with an error.
DONE_OK  The request is done and ok.
